      • isIncludedInPrice

        public boolean isIncludedInPrice()
        True if the tax is included in product price.

        If isIncludedInPrice is true, the product price is specified as a gross price and the tax is included in that price.

        If isIncludedInPrice is false, the product price is specified as a net price and the tax is added on top of that price.
